Git Commands

Clone/Download project
=> git clone https://github.com/shinderahul/tuts.git

To check repo status
=> git status

To Tracked/Add a single file
=> git add README.md

OR

To Tracked/Add all files
=> git add .

To unstage file to untrack
=> git rm --cached README.md

To commit file
=> git commit -m "Added style to header"

To push code
=> git push

To clear Terminal
=> cls

To check branch name
=> git branch

To restore back our changes
=> git restore style.css

To create new branch 
=> git checkout -b "develop"

To switch branch
=> git checkout master

To unsave in branch
=> git stash






Regular usage
git branch
git pull
git status
git add (fileName)
git status
git commit -m "Comment will come here"
git status
git push